   ======== SIGNUP =========
    1 - check holder in db
    2 - hash password
    3 - create user 
    4 - create publicKey and privateKey and save
    5 - generate tokens
    6 - get data return signup
   
   
    ======== LOGIN =========
    1 - check email in db
    2 - match password
    3 - create accessToken and refreshToken and save
    4 - generate tokens
    5 - get data return login

        ======== AUTHENTICATION =========
    1 - check userId missing
    2 - get accessToken
    3 - verify token
    4 - check user in db
    5 - check keyStore with this userId
    6 - return next()


